===Etymology===
From {{etyl|enm|en}} {{term|talken|lang=enm}}, {{term|talkien|lang=enm}}, from {{etyl|ang|en}} {{m|ang|*tealcian||to talk, chat}}, from {{etyl|gem-pro|en}} {{m|gem-pro|*talkōną||to talk, chatter}}, frequentative form of {{etyl|gem-pro|en}} {{m|gem-pro|*talōną||to count, recount, tell}}, from {{etyl|ine-pro|en}} {{m|ine-pro|*dol-}}, {{m|ine-pro|*del-||to aim, calculate, adjust, count}}, equivalent to {{suffix|tell|k|lang=en|nocat=1}}. Cognate with {{etyl|sco|-}} {{term|talk||to talk|lang=sco}}, {{etyl|nds|-}} {{term|taalken||to talk|lang=nds}}. Related also to {{etyl|da|-}} {{term|tale||to talk, speak|lang=da}}, {{etyl|sv|-}} {{term|tala||to talk, speak, say, chatter|lang=sv}}, {{etyl|is|-}} {{term|tala||to talk|lang=is}}, {{etyl|ang|-}} {{term|talian||to count, calculate, reckon, account, consider, think, esteem, value; argue; tell, relate; impute, assign|lang=ang}}. More at {{l|en|tale}}.

